ze-full wp-post-image" alt="《石器时代女王》的乔什·霍姆 (Josh Homme)" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Queens-of-the-Stone-Age-Josh-Homme-Photo-by-Bianca-de-Vilar_Redferns.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Queens-of-the-Stone-Age-Josh-Homme-Photo-by-Bianca-de-Vilar_Redferns-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Queens-of-the-Stone-Age-Josh-Homme-Photo-by-Bianca-de-Vilar_Redferns-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Queens-of-the-Stone-Age-Josh-Homme-Photo-by-Bianca-de-Vilar_Redferns-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Queens-of-the-Stone-Age-Josh-Homme-Photo-by-Bianca-de-Vilar_Redferns-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Queens-of-the-Stone-Age-Josh-Homme-Photo-by-Bianca-de-Vilar_Redferns-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/josh-homme">乔什·霍姆 (Josh Homme)</a>承诺，他将“卷起袖子”，这样下一张专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/queens-of-the-stone-age">Queens Of The Stone Age》</a>就不会让歌迷们等待太久。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/queens-of-the-stone-age-josh-homme-in-times-new-roman-tour-3454749">《石器时代的女王》：“这张专辑听起来就像活着的感觉一样残酷”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位主唱在<a href="https://open.spotify.com/show/5mx50pw8N4FnVOvcVpKpgT" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Dish</em>播客</a>上的一次新露面中讨论了新材料的计划，他回顾了乐队的巡演日期以及歌迷对他们最近作品的反应。</p><p>霍姆和公司。去年，他们发布了最新的 LP <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/queens-of-the-stone-age-in-times-new-room-review-3455962">《In Times New Roman…》</a> ，这张专辑的发行标志着他们的第八张录音室专辑，也是人们期待已久的 2017 年<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/queens-stone-age-villains-review-2128338">《Villains》的后续专辑。</a>然而，根据主唱的说法，乐队无意再等六年来放弃更多的材料。</p><p> “上一张唱片和这张唱片之间间隔了太多时间，”他（通过<a href="https://www.music-news.com/news/UK/175420/I-m-going-to-roll-my-sleeves-up-Queens-of-the-Stone-Age-issue-next-album-update" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>音乐新闻</em></a>）说道。 “我们的目标是创造东西并享受这个过程，所以我将卷起袖子直接投入其中。”</p><p>他还表达了对<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/foo-fighters">喷火战机</a>主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dave-grohl">戴夫·格罗尔（Dave Grohl）</a>的欣赏，并承认在他从事音乐行业的整个过程中，戴夫·格罗尔就像他的“兄弟”一样。 “在我的职业生涯中，没有人比戴夫为我做的更多，”霍姆说。 “他确实向全世界介绍了我和我巨大而无尽的才华，而且他一直像我的兄弟一样。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C8Up-cmPkgz/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924,30.41 556.869,30.41 M541,60.657 C535.114,60.657 530.342,55.887 530.342,50 C530.342,44.114 535.114,39.342 541,39.342 C546.887,39.342 551.658,44.1